<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٦١٧١ - مُعْتَمِرٌ، عَنِ ابْنِ عَوْنٍ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ الْحَسَنَ: مَا أَدْنَى مَا يَتَزَوَّجُ عَلَيْهِ الرَّجُلُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَزْنُ نَوَاةٍ مِنْ ذَهَبٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>